HEADWORD: Ltd.
<hw>Ltd.</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A term attached to the name of a
company that is organized to give its owners limited liability; it
corresponds to <altname>Inc.</altname> in the United States.</def>
<mark>[British]</mark> ⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> limited company, Ld.</syn>⟦br⟧
